common_issues.title: Workstream Summary Generation Failure Due to Model Access
common_issues.description: Users are unable to generate Workstream Summaries due to a 404 error indicating the Publisher Model `projects/pi3c3s-cloud-server/locations/us-east1/publishers/google/models/gemini-pro` is not found or inaccessible.  Verify project access to the specified Gemini Pro model. Ensure the model version is valid and the project has necessary permissions.

recommendations: Investigate and resolve the 'Workstream Summary Generation Failure Due to Model Access' error. This appears to be the primary issue affecting users and is related to project access for the Gemini Pro model.
Verify project permissions and ensure access to the specified Gemini Pro model (`projects/pi3c3s-cloud-server/locations/us-east1/publishers/google/models/gemini-pro`).
Check the validity of the Gemini Pro model version being used.
Provide more detailed error messages to users encountering the Workstream Summary generation issue, including potential troubleshooting steps.
